description:
Heartbreak Island - Season 1, Episode 3




The fallout from the first couple swap leaves some singles blindsided by the shock pairings, but the chance for revenge at the challenge could see some players sent packing from the island.

Secret Dates
It's not just on the island where the drama unfolds... We're sending each eliminated guy and girl off on a secret date around Fiji, to get the inside scoop on the developing relationships, the betrayals, and their reactions to leaving. Also, find out if love will blossom between any of the evictees.




Original Air Date: 13-Jun-2018
